{
  "stem": "9262.7",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We have to certify it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We are waiting for the brigadier to come in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this will be taken over to the SS.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they will eat it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So, he says, while they are feasting, we should have a little feast of ourselves.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they gave me a little bit of their broth as well.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then we had cows.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I said to one of them, cows give milk.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Can't we have a bit of milk?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, no, he says.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They've all got tuberculosis.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He says, we don't want to have that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He says, only fools, people who want to die, they will drink the milk.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We won't touch their milk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I worked there till the end of the liquidation of the Auschwitz concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it came about that, in January, before the Russian advance, the brigadier called us all up.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said to me, you will be in charge of the wagon with all the medicines, all the medical staff, like [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] syringes and injections and all different kinds what they give to the animals.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there will be a guard on top of the wagon.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we always traveled at night time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I took that wagon, which was loaded up with all the medicaments and all the instruments.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the German guard, who was a Yugoslavian fellow, young fellow, fairly cocky devil, always tried to put his bayonet onto my neck, you know, like poking me that he is there, which game was irritating.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was hurting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So out we came of Auschwitz, of the concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The sky was alight, just like daylight.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They put these flamethrowers through.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It lit the whole sky up.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
